.org/resource/Aurelio_Saffi\"}, {\"begin\": 2028, \"end\": 2033, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vette_(Star_Wars)\", \"score\": 0.876375122017715, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Vette\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vette_(Star_Wars)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vette_(Star_Wars)\"}, {\"begin\": 2046, \"end\": 2059, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carissa_Moore\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Carissa Moore\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carissa_Moore\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carissa_Moore\"}, {\"begin\": 2067, \"end\": 2082, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Teresa_Bonvalot\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Teresa Bonvalot\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Teresa_Bonvalot\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Teresa_Bonvalot\"}, {\"begin\": 2094, \"end\": 2101, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seiko_Matsuda\", \"score\": 0.9999999873807611, \"rank\": 1.2031434285164966e-08, \"text\": \"Matsuda\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seiko_Matsuda\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seiko_Matsuda\"}, {\"begin\": 2109, \"end\": 2112, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan\", \"score\": 0.9999998761727588, \"rank\": 1.2382654605526653e-07, \"text\": \"JPN\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan\"}, {\"begin\": 2187, \"end\": 2193, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tahiti\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.9393123425910603e-14, \"text\": \"Tahiti\", \"types\": [\"Q23442\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tahiti\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tahiti\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Some of the best surfers to have ever graced the water will be in the lineup at Teahupo'o.\", \"from\": 2195, \"to\": 2285, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Despite this being the second go-around for surfing at the Olympics, the waves in Tahiti will be very different than three years ago in Tokyo.\", \"from\": 2286, \"to\": 2428, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2368, \"end\": 2374, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tahiti\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.9393123425910603e-14, \"text\": \"Tahiti\", \"types\": [\"Q23442\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tahiti\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tahiti\"}, {\"begin\": 2422, \"end\": 2427, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.9999998724270053, \"rank\": 1.2757287473688925e-07, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Those with experience at this dangerous wave break and the strength to handle the harsh conditions of this massive pumping left will excel this time around.\", \"from\": 2429, \"to\": 2585, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Carissa Mooreis a multi-time World Champion and can never really be overlooked in any competition she enters.\", \"from\": 2587, \"to\": 2696, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"However, after taking the entire year off of WSL competition to prepare for this Olympic season, there are some unanswered questions surrounding Moore this week.\", \"from\": 2697, \"to\": 2858, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2842, \"end\": 2847, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alan_Moore\", \"score\": 0.9993966581854532, \"rank\": 0.0003826275488167587, \"text\": \"Moore\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q36180\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alan_Moore\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alan_Moore\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"While she did not have the hustle and bustle of the WSL season, it left an opening for her to travel to Tahiti more than her peers and practice in the water.\", \"from\": 2859, \"to\": 3016, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2963, \"end\": 2969, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tahiti\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.9393123425910603e-14, \"text\": \"Tahiti\", \"types\": [\"Q23442\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tahiti\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tahiti\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In the past three years, she has placed fifth in each WSL competition held at Teahupo'o.\", \"from\": 3017, \"to\": 3105, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"John John Florenceis known as the King of Pipeline.\", \"from\": 3107, \"to\": 3158, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He excels in Hawaii but can charge on any big wave he finds.\", \"from\": 3159, \"to\": 3219, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3172, \"end\": 3178, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hawaii\", \"score\": 0.9999999999363354, \"rank\": 4.832125864761717e-11, \"text\": \"Hawaii\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hawaii\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hawaii\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This year at the SHISEIDO Tahiti Pro presented by Outerknown, Florence took second place.\", \"from\": 3220, \"to\": 3309, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3282, \"end\": 3290, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Florence\", \"score\": 0.9999999808865143, \"rank\": 1.9113696243281224e-08, \"text\": \"Florence\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Florence\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Florence\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He is a former World Champion and seems to be surfing at his very best these days following some injury-filled years.\", \"from\": 3310, \"to\": 3427, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3325, \"end\": 3339, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_championship\", \"score\": 0.6529400869388219, \"rank\": 0.5315118877081053, \"text\": \"World Champion\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_championship\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_championship\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"His goal was always to make the Olympic team and despite not finishing on the podium in 2021, these waves in Tahtit are a much better fit for his style.\", \"from\": 3428, \"to\": 3580, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Vahine Fierro is a local girl who got the call to serve as a Wildcard fill-in at her home break of Teahupo'o at the WSL event held there in May.\", \"from\": 3582, \"to\": 3726, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3698, \"end\": 3701, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Surf_League\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.1794774892885794e-50, \"text\": \"WSL\", \"types\": [\"Q623109\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Surf_League\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Surf_League\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She showed her home cooking and won the competition, making her the first Tahitian wildcard to claim a victory at Teahupo'o.\", \"from\": 3727, \"to\": 3851, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"She will be on hand during this Olympic competition to perhaps once again play spoiler and show just why they now call her \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cQueen of Teahupo'o.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d  Stay tuned for the competition window to open on July 27 and round 1 to kick off shortly after that.\", \"from\": 3852, \"to\": 4102, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00c2\\u00a9 2026Minute Media-All Rights Reserved.\", \"from\": 4104, \"to\": 4144, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The content on this site is for entertainment and educational purposes only.\", \"from\": 4145, \"to\": 4221, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Betting and gambling content is intended for individuals 21+ and is based on individual commentators' opinions and not that of Minute Media or its affiliates and related brands.\", \"from\": 4222, \"to\": 4399, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"All picks and predictions are suggestions only and not a guarantee of success or profit.\", \"from\": 4400, \"to\": 4488, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"If you or someone you know has a gambling problem, crisis counseling and referral services can be accessed by calling 1-800-GAMBLER.\", \"from\": 4489, \"to\": 4621, \"entities\": []}]}"